{"tid":1322193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有2條超級惡法要小心 政府可能研究緊","createTime":"2019-07-16T01:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T06:09:09.000Z","uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8f316fb8e506daee5f517ccf491a010becf5c3e6","tid":1322193,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:14:16.000Z","msg":"《緊急情況規例條例》<br />\n在行政長官會同行政會議認為屬緊急情況或危害公安的情況時，行政長官會同行政會議可訂立任何他認為合乎公眾利益的規例。<br />\n呢條惡法可以取締任何媒體, 包括連登, 蘋果日報, 立場新聞...<br />\n仲可以無需理由拘捕任何人<br />\n<br />\n仲有條係基本法18條<br />\n18條賦與中央人民政府在全國人大常委會「因」香港特別行政區發生「不能控制的危及國家統一或安全的動亂」時，便可「決定」香港特別行政區進入緊急狀態，「可發佈命令將有關全國性法律在香港特別行政區實施」"},{"pid":"85f17702981e65c9ae91cef1f4f341e7bf4f9e0c","tid":1322193,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:15:29.000Z","msg":"林鄭會以&quot;死人&quot;為下台點， 下任特首會清算警方以挽回民望<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322186\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322186</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dcc06ba523aff499c94df92cf7e5568e008cc751","tid":1322193,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85f17702981e65c9ae91cef1f4f341e7bf4f9e0c","tid":1322193,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:15:29.000Z","msg":"林鄭會以&quot;死人&quot;為下台點， 下任特首會清算警方以挽回民望<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322186\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322186</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb253dcb214b3ea6a5aec8940fdad0c1f11a7fcf","tid":1322193,"uid":19294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:21:51.000Z","msg":"721嘅和理非入嚟，你地係保護勇武嘅最後一道防線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322165</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d8d2d024316927f03de8eb6c9749397901bdf792","tid":1322193,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-1